            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Domitius Epaphro<supplied reason="lost">ditus</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="2"/>is anno primo magi<supplied reason="lost">steri</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="3"/>cum base et hasta pri<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="4"/>isdem pridie <expan><abbr>Non</abbr><ex>as</ex></expan> lu<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">ta</supplied><lb break="no" n="5"/>bernas IX et cibar<supplied reason="lost">ia</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Das Stück scheint verschollen zu sein. Fundstelle: Heiligtum, das offenbar dem Mars gewidmet war. Lesung nach G. Alföldy.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography">
                <listBibl><bibl>G. Alföldy, Römische Statuen in Venetia et Histria. Epigraphische Quellen (Heidelberg 1984) 94, Nr. 71.</bibl><bibl/></listBibl>
            </div>
